data: Arverne Library was located at Beach 75th Street and Rockaway Beach Blvd, Arverne, from 1915-1921. It moved to 488 Beach 66th St. in 1922, and was there until 1935.From 1951-1964, it was located at 339 Beach 54th St., until it moved into its current location at 312 Beach 54th St, Arverne in 1964.
14-01 Astoria Boulevard, Long Island City, NY 11102
Astoria Library was first opened on February 28, 1899 at 112 Fulton Ave, Astoria, NY. In 1904, it moved to its current location at 1401 Astoria Blvd.

The Auburndale library first opened in 1930 at 199-10 32nd Ave, Auburndale. It was located at 200-15 32nd Ave from 1937-1952, at 29-09 Francis Lewis Blvd. 1952-1969, and 25-55 Francis Lewis Blvd. from 1969 to the present.

Baisley Park first opened on June 25, 1935 at 116-03 Sutphin Blvd, Baisley Park, and was at that location until 1970. On Dec 14, 1970, it moved to its present location, 117-11 Sutphin Blvd., Baisley Park.
Bayside has moved four times; 1906-1911, Bell Ave, near Palace Ave, Bayside: 1912-1934, at Elsie Pl. and 1st St: 1935-1965, 39-28 Bell Blvd, Bayside: and 1965-its present location.
The Bellerose Branch was first opened on February 27, 1978.
The Briarwood Branch was first opened on April 14, 1975.
16-26 Cross Bay Boulevard, Broad Channel, NY 11693
The Broad Channel Branch has been open since the summer of 1990–present.

The Broadway branch first opened in 1906 at 37-19 Broadway Astoria, New York. It moved five subsequent times until it was relocated to 40-20 Broadway Astoria, on April 28, 1958, where it remains today.
The Cambria heights branch first opened in July, 1949 on 220-20 Linden Blvd, Cambria Heights. Since 2006, the branch has been at 218-13 Linden Blvd, Cambria Heights.
The Corona branch had its first days at 13 Locust Street, Corona, from 1912-1913. It has since moved five times to its present location at 38-23 104th St, in March 1969.
25-01 Jackson Avenue, Long Island City, NY 11101

The Douglaston Library was in operation from 1914-1934.

The Far Rockaway Branch has been open from August 1904-present, and is currently located at 1637 Central Avenue, Far Rockaway.
The Flushing Branch first opened in January, 1902 at Jamaica Ave and Jagger Ave. It moved 3 times until it settled at its present location in 1998 at 41-17 Main St, Flushing, New York.
The Forest Hills branch first opened in 1915 at 1 Station Sq, Forest Hills, NY. It moved 5 times until settling in its present location at 108-19 71st Ave in 1947.
193-20 Horace Harding Expressway, Fresh Meadows, NY 11365
The Fresh Meadows branch was located at 195-13 69th Ave, from 1949-1958, until it moved to 193-20 Horace Harding Expressway, Fresh Meadows, in 1958, and still remains today.
The Glen Oaks Branch has had two locations: From 1950-1956, it was at 256-25 Union Turnpike, Glen Oaks, NY, and from 1956-present is was just down the street at 256-04 Turnpike.
The Glendale Library has had four locations, opening first in April 1911 at 123 Edison in Glendale, and presently occupying a location at 78-60 73rd Pl, Glendale, NY.
Hillcrest Library has been open from 1980-present at 187-05 Turnpike, Hillcrest.
The Hollis Branch has moved seven times, and has been open since 1906. It currently is located at 202-05 Hillside Ave, Hollis, NY.
The Howard Beach location first opened in May 1963. It moved to its present location at 92-06 156th Ave in November 1978.
The Jackson Heights branch has moved five times. It was opened in 1918, and has been at its current location at 35-51 81st St, Jackson Heights, since 1954.
Kew Garden Hills Branch was formerly the Vleigh Branch. Is has been open since 1998 at 72-33 Vleigh Place.
Langston Hughes Library first opened in 1969, and was open at that location until 1999. It moved to its current location at 100-01 Northern Boulevard in 1999.
The Laurelton was first opened in 1936. It has moved 2 times, the 2nd move in 1954, was to its present location at 134-26 225th St., Laurelton.
The Lefferts Library opened in 1975 at 103-34 Lefferts Boulevard, and remains there today.
The Lefrak City was first opened in December 1966, and moved to its present location at 98-30 57th Ave, Corona in 1997.
